data.title: Great Take Out
data.text: The take & bake meals are honestly SO worth it. I cannot spend the amt of money the owner does and make as great of a meal. The meals are made for 2 or 4 people and truly worth it. She will be opening a restaurant soon according to the papers and I am very excited to be trying her food.

data.title: Amazing
data.text: I met the chef & owner and am truly happy she has a storefront (Catering & Take & Bake Meals). She has WONDERFUL prepared meals to go, and you just heat them. What makes her different is the food is GOURMET at a VERY affordable price. Where else can I get a meal FULLY prepared for around $10-13 dollars for 2-3 servings! The lasagna is AMAZING as is the hashbrown casserole. I found her storefront my strolling down the main street area and can say this was an A-1 Find!! She also has a catering business for larger groups of which if our family picnic is happening this year, I will be using her services!!
